Prove that, after the procedure $\text{INITIALIZE-PREFLOW}(G, S)$ terminates, we have $s.e \le -|f^*|$, where $f^*$ is a maximum flow for $G$.   We apply the definition of excess flow (equation $\text{(26.14)}$) to the initial preflow $f$ created by $\text{INITIALIZE-PREFLOW}$ (equation $\text{(26.15)}$) to obtain  \begin{align}
